  "text": "As instillation of SCFA in the colon has a trophic effect, it seems reasonable to infer that fibre or non-digested carbohydrates which are broken down to SCFA in the colon should also have this effect [CITATION_1] . Indeed, pectin and guar have been found to increase mucosal DNA content in the rat colon [CITATION_2] .",
